inPassword`, and `loginErrorMessage` directly, which preserves immediate UI feedback for login field edits and invalid login attempts.\",\n92:         \"The Harmony onboarding page keeps the same static content flow with no permission prompts.\",\n93:         \"`OnboardingStore` keeps this seeded slide list as pure local data with no permission flow.\",\n94:         \"The translated login route uses plain `TextInput` controls and keeps this no-permission behavior.\",\n95:         \"The translated login fields stay as plain text inputs with placeholder text only and do not introduce settings/configuration toggles.\"\n96:       ],\n97:       \"acceptanceEvidence\": [\n98:         \"Replace broad endpoints with precise target functions, types, resources, or tests before closing the group.\"\n99:       ],\n100:       \"riskHints\": [\n101:         \"current evidence uses broad shell/root/whole-file endpoints\"\n102:       ],\n103:       \"matrixRows\": [\n104:         {\n105:           \"kind\": \"source-feature\",\n106:           \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-login-b030a7b1f9-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom\",\n107:           \"featureName\": \"Image viewing, bitmap/exif handling, zoom, preview, or gallery display behavior.\",\n108:           \"sourcePath\": \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginScreen.kt\",\n109:           \"importance\": \"critical\",\n110:           \"plannedPhase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login\",\n111:           \"status\": \"not-applicable\",\n112:           \"parityLevel\": \"not-applicable\",\n113:           \"verdict\": \"complete\",\n114:           \"reasons\": [\n115:             \"not-applicable has source/notes explanation\"\n116:           ],\n117:           \"targetEndpoints\": [\n118:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/login/login_page.cj\"\n119:           ],\n120:           \"tests\": [\n121:             \"entry/src/test/cangjie